      "span_text": "Microstrip line to WG transitions have been heavily researched. Among them, a solder-joint-free inline microstrip to conventional WG transition [CITATION_1] , offering S 11 < −10 dB and S 21 > −1.1 dB, from 8.5-9.5 GHz (11% measured rel. bandwidth), albeit for a relatively low r = 3.8 substrate."
